 -3 \, x_{1} &  -  & 5 \, x_{2} &  -  & x_{3} & = & -4 \\
 4 \, x_{1} &  +  & 3 \, x_{2} &  -  & 6 \, x_{3} & = & -2 \\
 -x_{1} &  -  & x_{2} &  +  & x_{3} & = & 0 \\
 \end{matrix}\] 

Write an augmented matrix corresponding to this system.

 \end{exerciseStatement}
 \begin{exerciseAnswer} \[\left(\begin{array}{rrr|r}
-3 & -1 & 7 & 4 \\
-3 & -5 & -1 & -4 \\
4 & 3 & -6 & -2 \\
-1 & -1 & 1 & 0
\end{array}\right)\] \end{exerciseAnswer}
 \end{exercise}

